PCWorld is the most widely-read computer or business magazine among all purchase

including the 2005 Maggie Award for Best Computer Magazine, PCWorld is targeted to meet 
the informational needs of Tech-Savvy Managers, both at work and at home. 

With its monthly Reviews and Rankings backed by the PCWorld Test Center, news,
